WE live in an era where footballers lives are more documented and followed than ever before. Mostly when they are in camp, the stars are always in their club colours/tracksuits. However, when they get a chance, they always showcase their fresh sartorial choices reveal their true style on social media. Here we look at one of Real Madrid most stylish man Karim Benzema. The striker often showcases an impressive catalogue of his favourite labels like Supreme, Balenciaga, and Gucci. Undoubtedly, Benzema has nailed every look, with his outfits rarely missing the mark. Take a look…  